Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.11,0:00:44.17,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,うまいこと泳ぐな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.37,0:01:10.53,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,さてと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.64,0:01:26.60,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お　悪いな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.88,0:01:28.68,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,煙たかったか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.42,0:01:36.67,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,やけに冷たいな　水に入ってたにしろ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.17,0:01:39.98,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,涌太
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.23,0:01:47.22,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,涌太 どうしたの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.13,0:01:50.95,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あの　一体何が…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.96,0:01:53.21,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いや　申し訳ない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.16,0:01:55.78,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,タバコの煙吸っちまったみたいで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.70,0:01:59.48,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,母ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.79,0:02:06.74,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,今日もたくさん取れたわね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.85,0:02:10.69,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,さあ　もう帰るわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.56,0:02:14.13,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あの　
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.04,0:02:15.63,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何か
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.78,0:02:19.26,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,その子　泳ぎは達者だが　
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.78,0:02:21.46,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,走るのは少々不得手では
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.01,0:02:25.24,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,だったら何なの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.35,0:02:29.98,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,異様に　喉の渇きを訴えたりは？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.11,0:02:37.87,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何が 言いたいんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.74,0:02:59.35,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,幾つか　われわれ蟲師の記録と符合する点がありましてね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.78,0:03:04.42,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,低い体温　言葉の遅れ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.56,0:03:08.95,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,稀に　水掻きのあるものも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.61,0:03:13.04,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それがなんだってんです？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.33,0:03:15.40,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,妙な言いがかりは…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.45,0:03:16.82,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それらの原因が蟲なら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.43,0:03:19.07,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,影響を薄める薬があります
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.80,0:03:23.77,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,やはり　他の子と様子が違うのは
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:26.67,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いろいろと不安なんじゃないですか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.33,0:03:40.70,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,水を掻いてんのか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.60,0:03:44.38,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,夢の中でも泳いでんのかね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.50,0:04:11.22,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あの子の中には　雨蠱という蟲がいます
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.57,0:04:18.37,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,個体としては　肉眼では捉えられないほど小さなもの
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.88,0:04:24.19,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それが雨に紛れ川へ流れ込むと
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.60,0:04:29.13,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,群れて碧い巨大魚のような姿で川を下り
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:33.84,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,やがて海に出て　子を成す
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.05,0:04:38.71,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それがまた水蒸気に紛れ　
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.49,0:04:41.21,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,雨となり　山河に降り注ぐ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.01,0:04:46.83,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そうして生きているものに過ぎないが
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.37,0:04:53.17,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,川を下るときに　群れの一部が淵などに取り残されると
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.91,0:04:58.91,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,魚に食われないように 山椒魚などの体内に寄生する
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.59,0:05:03.22,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,が　ごく稀に
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.24,0:05:06.95,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,溺れて仮死状態となった人に寄生することもある
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.26,0:05:11.86,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そうなると　蘇生はするが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.67,0:05:16.34,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,息子さんのような影響が残り　完全に抜くことはできない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:23.76,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,大水が起こると　濁流に乗じて海へ出ようと
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.14,0:05:25.65,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,自ら抜け出ることもあるが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.54,0:05:28.00,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いつ起こるとも分からない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.17,0:05:34.38,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,まずは暫く　この薬で様子を見てください
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.03,0:06:15.79,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,涌太
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.83,0:06:24.57,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,涌太
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.74,0:06:29.76,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,夜は来ちゃだめだって言ってるでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.35,0:06:34.43,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,また　水の夢を見たのね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.04,0:07:00.82,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,母ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.52,0:07:05.04,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,すごいの取れたわね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.71,0:07:13.45,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ほら
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.39,0:07:20.04,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.55,0:07:21.75,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,入れてやんねぇぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.68,0:07:26.10,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あいつ　体が魚みてぇに冷てぇんだってさ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.56,0:07:27.65,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,人の子じゃねぇんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.28,0:07:29.09,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,気味悪い
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.37,0:07:37.09,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.30,0:07:40.75,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,うわ　でっけぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.71,0:07:44.49,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,向こう　たくさんいる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.80,0:07:47.90,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,一緒遊ぼう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.77,0:07:53.27,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そっち
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.05,0:07:57.14,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,下手くそ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.99,0:08:02.07,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あれ　お前　そんな体冷たくねぇな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.16,0:08:04.89,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,本当だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.67,0:08:07.23,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,誰が冷てぇとか言ったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.83,0:08:08.37,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,さあ　
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.14,0:08:15.27,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ね　母ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.10,0:08:16.91,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.54,0:08:19.27,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,川はどこから来る？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:22.69,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,山奥の谷から流れてくるのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.21,0:08:26.16,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,谷の水　どこから来る？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.82,0:08:29.03,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,空の雲から降ってくるのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.00,0:08:32.02,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,じゃあ　空の雲は？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.42,0:08:36.68,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,えっと　あっそう　海から生まれるのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:38.88,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,海？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.84,0:08:41.85,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,この川が行き着くところよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.83,0:08:44.83,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,たくさん水があるところ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.99,0:08:48.35,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,たくさん？どれぐらい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.17,0:08:52.51,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,母さんもまだ見たことないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.27,0:08:55.31,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,見渡す限り水なんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:08:57.31,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,へえ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.59,0:09:03.00,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,じゃあ　海も川も雨も雲も全部一緒？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.51,0:09:08.79,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そうよ　形は違うけど　みんな同じなの
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.03,0:09:12.01,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そうか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.26,0:09:19.21,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,どうしたの
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.23,0:09:24.37,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何でもないわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.55,0:09:38.33,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,元気そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.48,0:09:41.45,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あ　煙のおじさん
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.28,0:09:43.12,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,おじさん…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.38,0:09:46.09,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,もう　煙はいやじゃねぇのか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.02,0:09:48.69,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,うん　そんなに
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.99,0:09:58.26,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,薬が効いたみたいだな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.23,0:09:59.93,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,はい　
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:02.99,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,体温もずいぶん上がりましたし
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.00,0:10:06.85,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,以前は日に一升も水を欲しがりましたが
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.33,0:10:09.43,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,今は七合ほどに減ってきてます
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.64,0:10:11.52,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そりゃよかった
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.42,0:10:13.78,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ありがとうございます
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.77,0:10:17.55,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あの薬　またいただけますか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:22.61,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,言っておくが　恐らくこれ以上の効果は望めない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.19,0:10:26.05,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,蟲が抜けたわけではないのでね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.25,0:10:30.94,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,本来　人に寄生するものではないから
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:33.29,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,人とはそう深く結びつかないが
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.49,0:10:37.51,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,山椒魚などは　寄生されて数年たつと
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:39.31,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,同化して水に消えてしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.71,0:10:43.93,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そういう　厄介なものなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.58,0:10:46.33,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.81,0:10:49.52,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,でもあの子は大丈夫なんでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.89,0:10:55.07,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,恐らく　薬で影響を抑えながら現状を保てるはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:11:00.06,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それでよければ　また頃合を見て薬を持ってくる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.69,0:11:03.73,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ま　薬代は安くしとくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.95,0:11:09.86,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そうね　それで充分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.39,0:11:14.03,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,おじさん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.21,0:11:14.96,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,おじさんじゃねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.64,0:11:17.85,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,次　いつ来る？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.17,0:11:21.38,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,んん　秋口だ　
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.37,0:11:25.28,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,じゃあな　もう溺れんなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.44,0:11:28.77,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,おれ　溺れたことないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.62,0:11:31.80,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,嘘付け　忘れてんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.52,0:11:34.53,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,おい　涌太
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.87,0:11:37.95,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,じゃあ　またね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.35,0:12:00.93,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,涌太　
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.09,0:12:03.16,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,中へ入ってなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.21,0:12:20.88,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,どうしたの
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.47,0:12:25.06,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,喉が乾いたの　川は駄目よ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.78,0:12:27.63,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,行かなきゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:31.98,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何言って　待ちなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.18,0:12:35.12,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,涌太
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.64,0:12:47.18,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,涌太　どこ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.71,0:12:51.76,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ギンコさん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.43,0:12:54.07,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ここらが長雨だと聞いてな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.88,0:12:57.54,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,このままだと　鉄砲水が来る
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.62,0:13:03.07,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,危険も伴うが　上手くいきゃ雨蠱を抜けるかもしれん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.13,0:13:06.13,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,やるなら手を貸す
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.45,0:13:16.70,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ごめんね　我慢してね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.18,0:13:20.77,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,でも　こうすればあんたも　
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.45,0:13:23.56,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,きっと他の子たちと同じになれる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.41,0:13:28.48,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,村の皆に認めてもらえる子に
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.05,0:13:46.99,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,じっとして　危ないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.86,0:13:49.85,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,行かなきゃ　
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.17,0:13:54.14,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,もう行かなきゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.15,0:13:56.60,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何言ってるの　
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.33,0:13:58.21,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,止めなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.28,0:14:03.89,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,絶対に　絶対にどこへもやらないから
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.75,0:15:22.07,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,涌太　起きて　朝よ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.43,0:15:30.70,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,涌太　返事して
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.73,0:15:34.73,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,母ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.35,0:15:37.43,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,良かった
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.58,0:15:41.82,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,母ちゃん　どうしたの
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.34,0:15:48.03,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,雨怖かったね　もう怖くないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.95,0:15:52.94,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ええ　そうね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.82,0:15:57.75,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,雨蠱は抜けた…のか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.15,0:16:04.23,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ　母ちゃん　喉乾いた
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.97,0:16:06.55,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そう　
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.23,0:16:10.74,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,川の水は泥が混ざっちゃったから
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.32,0:16:12.96,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,山のほうの井戸まで行こうか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.99,0:16:28.54,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,未だ喉の渇きを訴える 抜き切っていないのか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.36,0:16:37.15,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,どうしたんです
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.20,0:16:40.56,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,おかしい　体がひどく熱い
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.14,0:16:43.04,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,とにかく水を
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.44,0:16:46.31,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,涌太
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.75,0:16:58.48,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,涌太
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.61,0:17:13.41,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,涌…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.93,0:17:17.62,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,どこ　
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.13,0:17:20.21,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,どこへ消えたの
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.71,0:17:25.51,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,どこなの
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.03,0:17:36.18,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ　母ちゃん　
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.37,0:17:39.45,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,川　どこから来る？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.31,0:17:45.06,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,山の奥の谷から流れて来るのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.16,0:17:49.63,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,谷の水　どこから来る？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.83,0:17:53.00,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,空の雲から降ってくるのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.60,0:17:57.69,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,じゃあ　空の雲は？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.27,0:18:00.70,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,海から生まれるのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.49,0:18:03.22,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,海？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.32,0:18:09.01,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,この川の行き着く所よ　たくさん水のある所
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.42,0:18:19.53,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,どうして　あの子は
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.63,0:18:29.69,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あの子は　自分は溺れたことはないと言っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.74,0:18:34.76,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,川で溺れたのは
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.41,0:18:37.00,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あんたか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.32,0:18:42.90,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.85,0:18:52.33,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あれは　あの子の生まれる十月ほど前のことです
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.10,0:18:57.00,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,なんだか今日は流れが速いな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.03,0:19:00.00,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,山で雨が降ったのかしら
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.98,0:19:11.58,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,気が付くと　私は岸にいました
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.33,0:19:14.37,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,けれど　夫は
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.19,0:19:17.96,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,深みの底で見つかりました　
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.54,0:19:25.10,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,その後　私は夫の子を身ごもっていることに気づきました
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.87,0:19:33.26,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,腹の中で無事でいてくれたことに 心底感謝しました
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.13,0:19:38.55,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,もう一息だよ　頑張って　
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.51,0:19:40.15,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.11,0:19:48.89,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,タキさん　気の毒だけど　
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.03,0:19:57.65,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,冷たい赤児でした
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.84,0:20:00.52,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,けれど　
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.23,0:20:07.42,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,その子は確かに生きていました
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.94,0:20:12.43,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,皆　恐ろしいと言ったけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.48,0:20:14.85,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,私は嬉しかった
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.57,0:20:21.76,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,普通でないなりに　これまで生きてくれてたんです
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.72,0:20:27.63,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,どうして　今になって…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.12,0:20:34.21,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,胎児は腹の中で水に浸されていて　
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.41,0:20:39.41,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,人よりも蛙や山椒魚　水の生き物に近いという
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.05,0:20:45.23,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あの子はその段階で雨蠱に寄生された
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.35,0:20:50.73,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そして　そのまま体内で成長していくうちに
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.49,0:20:55.63,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,分類できないほど深く深く一体化してしまった
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.22,0:21:02.07,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,私が　私がそんなものに憑かれたせいで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.62,0:21:07.33,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あの子が腹の中で無事だったのは
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.22,0:21:11.48,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,まず　あんたが雨蠱に寄生されて蘇生したからだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.21,0:21:16.93,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,でなけりゃ　二人とも生きてはいなかったろう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.06,0:21:20.93,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あいつは生きた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.50,0:21:25.81,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,確かにここに　
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.65,0:21:28.38,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,生きていた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.30,0:21:38.35,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,じゃあ　海も川も雨も雲も　全部一緒？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.18,0:21:46.45,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そうよ　形は違っても　皆同じなの
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.64,0:21:56.18,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,涌太　あんた今どこにいる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.19,0:22:05.15,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,川かしら　海かしら　雨かしら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.81,0:22:11.68,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,どうしたの　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.30,0:22:15.68,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,もう怖くないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.01,0:22:35.03,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そうだね　あんたはどこにでもいるんだものね
